verbose_text: In line with the idea that mTOR signaling stimulates de novo fatty acid synthesis, we found that the levels of polyunsaturated fatty acids (AA and DHA in MEFs and HUH7, LA in HUH7) originating from the uptake or processing of essential fatty acids (LA : AA; alpha-linolenic acid :D HA), were increased upon mTOR inhibition (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY A-S3I).
evidence: mTOR signaling stimulates de novo fatty acid
